{"tid":1360074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［夢境］有狗隻自殺不遂","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:52:51.000Z","uid":119729,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4086a239a0160fe1f8c3f391e9668de54d61d516","tid":1360074,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:25:33.000Z","msg":"借朋友連登戶口開<br />\n<br />\n以下內容全為老作，如有雷同實屬巧合<br />\n<br />\n有鄰居係狗公狗嫂<br />\n我老母係淺藍人士，平時同佢地有計傾<br />\n<br />\n自從反送中事件<br />\n樓下附近有人貼佢地兩公婆資料<br />\n而都KEEP住有人撕有人貼<br />\n<br />\n到左尋晚有救護員上黎佢地單位<br />\n我全家人（仲有好多戶人）睇住隻狗上左擔架送院<br />\n<br />\n今日我當然叫老母去關心下人地<br />\n狗嫂對所有野避而不答，淨係話多謝關心<br />\n<br />\n大家估下隻狗發生咩事拿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0ef16e49acaa203ca7de6b6c75924cd9eae2c5","tid":1360074,"uid":27146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"飲大左姐"},{"pid":"59f09e4de152e4313fa355c9aefb01492244a907","tid":1360074,"uid":168444,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"仔囡睇唔過眼老豆割佢地老豆.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n席"},{"pid":"966932036c70ff0138317b61856427ef9f615a82","tid":1360074,"uid":54303,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:28:25.000Z","msg":"香港警察 吞槍自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3339d12882eb50e88ee181ed04e112dc12ac8d","tid":1360074,"uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"966932036c70ff0138317b61856427ef9f615a82","tid":1360074,"uid":54303,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:28:25.000Z","msg":"香港警察 吞槍自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"推到有返果幾張吞槍連橫圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba0e9a73ba187fc23d577ca69d5debfbcd762d2","tid":1360074,"uid":73443,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"rep